item.title: CVE-2018-1934|2024-08-05T04:14:39.224Z -- ibm -- cognos%20business%20intelligence
item.description: IBM Cognos Business Intelligence 10.2.2 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts. IBM X-Force ID: 153179.
